'''International Conference on Differential Geometric Methods in Theoretical Physics''' are [[congress]]es held every few years on the subject of [[Differential geometry|Differential geometric method]]s in [[Theoretical physics]]. Lectures, seminars, and discussions are held in different universities throughout the world, every few years, and a book compilation is published thereafter consisting of the papers submitted and discussed at the conference.
